        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'It was an important day. I felt my body tense and seize multiple times, as if I were an old machine with outdated servos.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 21,
        "ActionId": 21,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'It was all because of a message from Commandant several days prior.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 22,
        "ActionId": 22,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Command Central', 3: 'After careful consideration from the Command Central, we have decided to replenish Gray Raven\\'s ranks, and start preparations for combat operations.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 23,
        "ActionId": 23,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Many more bureaucratic entries followed, but my attention was solely focused on the short, curt notice.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 24,
        "ActionId": 24,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Two reinforcing teammates were coming over, both with groundside combat experience. That is to say, we were combat-ready.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 25,
        "ActionId": 25,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'I felt joy at the turn of events, but also worry about what Gray Raven would turn into.'}"
